y voiced dialogue</strong> for your wing mate Amanda and the four Karens</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8-bit retro-inspired soundtrack</strong> hearkens to the glory days of console gaming</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beautiful pixel art</strong> crafted frame-by-frame</p></li></ul>",
